---
title: Garlicky Chicken with Tomatoes & Olives plus Couscous & Scallions
description: For this Mediterranean-style meal, you'll make a bold sauce from crushed tomatoes, olives, and scallions—the perfect pairing for garlicky seared chicken cutlets. Serve the saucy chicken over a bed of buttered springy couscous and sprinkle with scallion greens for bright crunch. Best of all, the whole meal comes together in a speedy 30 minutes.
